    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Yes. No parsing is required:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-bash prettyprint-override\"><code>$ jshell --feedback=silent -  &lt;&lt;&lt; 'System.out.println(System.getProperty(&quot;java.io.tmpdir&quot;))'\n/var/folders/k0/n6p7cm714pj6xpsd_ngcdht80000gn/T/\n% jshell --feedback=silent -  &lt;&lt;&lt; 'System.out.println(System.getProperty(&quot;java.ext.dirs&quot;))' \nnull\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
